# Root-level safety net for the monorepo (backend/ + frontend/ each have their own too)
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
dist/
**/dist/

# Never commit secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
!**/.env.example

# Internal prompt / spec docs (keep README.md and DEPLOYMENT.md)
*PROMPT*.md
**/ADVANCED_BACKEND_PROMPT.md
**/ADVANCED_FRONTEND_PROMPT.md
**/UI_KIT_DESIGN_SYSTEM.md

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
